@startuml
title Sequence Diagram - Login Studente

actor Studente as S
boundary GUI_Login as GUI
control LoginController as LC
entity StudentPostgresDAO as DAO
database PostgreSQL as DB

S -> GUI : Inserisce username/password
GUI -> LC : onLogin(username, password)
LC -> DAO : validateUser(username, password)
DAO -> DB : SELECT * FROM studenti WHERE username=? AND password=?
DB --> DAO : ResultSet
DAO --> LC : boolean (validazione)
LC --> GUI : esito login
GUI --> S : Login riuscito / fallito

@enduml


